OL,6,FConsumer confidence has fallen sharply
OL,7,Fin "not encouraging news" for the
OL,8,FGovernment as households "nervously"
OL,9,Fawait next month's autumn Budget,
OL,10,Faccording to a long-running survey.
OL,12,FGfK's Consumer Confidence Index fell
OL,13,Fseven points in September to minus 20,
OL,14,Fwith significant drops in predictions
OL,15,Ffor personal finances and the general
OL,16,Feconomy over the coming year.
