OL,3,CConsumer confidence falls sharply as
OL,4,Chouseholds 'nervously' await Budget
OL,6,FExpectations for the general economy
OL,7,Fover the next 12 months fell by 12
OL,8,Fpoints to minus 27, while the forecast
OL,9,Ffor personal finances is down nine
OL,10,Fpoints to minus three.
OL,12,FThe major purchase index, an indicator
OL,13,Fof confidence in buying big ticket
OL,14,Fitems, is down 10 points on last month
OL,15,Fto minus 23, five points higher than a
OL,16,Fyear ago.
